          { question: "Can the taxi pick me up at the Ile de Groix ferry terminal?", answer: "Yes, your driver waits at the exit of the Lorient maritime terminal (Quai de Rohan) when you return from Ile de Groix. Provide the ferry arrival time when booking." }
